title: TeraCopy_Portable_2.3_Multilingual.paf.exe
description:
File Copying Accelerator.


TeraCopy (Extract and run TeraCopyPortable.
You can replace Explorer copy and move files handler with TeraCopy by editing TeraCopyPortable.ini with ShellIntegration=true.
To bypass clean-up message: edit TeraCopyPortable.ini with CleanUpMessage=false.
Settings of installed TeraCopy should be preserved.
Launcher will wait until the last TeraCopy window closed.Portable)
